class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c621615b569e9560fd4bf836441ac6d54e34d1b","tid":1439553,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:27:37.000Z","msg":"我作為大埔人真心建議可以轉場，出面空場真係有大搜捕風險，保守實力更重要。<br />\n今日我見出面真係人影都唔多隻，大家要出既都要小心。"},{"pid":"3b426a61c6188799427fb1c07d036625e6b0790f","tid":1439553,"uid":51064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:29:31.000Z","msg":"會去機場既手足！<br />\n可以叫旅客follow ig @freehk_ <br />\n入面有唔同既英文文宣！可以俾佢地搭車睇同之後繼續follow up 香港既新聞！！！！！"},{"pid":"ee8f3e1e0dc294705812c03c363e8b41efde7976","tid":1439553,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:29:54.000Z","msg":"要幫福建狗扣獨立帽子<br />\n<br />\n機場見"},{"pid":"f24a0b7029c8e34c1f5292271b5c3a7897b1611a","tid":1439553,"uid":160247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQyY76m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQyY76m.jpg&h=31560105&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家記住佢，梁凌杰先生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gJfpjfH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgJfpjfH.jpg&h=11f54868&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n請大家記住佢，盧曉欣同學。<br />\n仲有鄔小姐，麥小姐，仲有其他為香港死既烈士。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知道大家都身心俱疲，好重好重既無力感，我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但一日抗爭未完，一日仲有人行出黎，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地都仲有希望架<br />\n</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抖一陣好啦，我地要繼續行出黎，唔好比同路人感到孤單，更加要對得住死去既烈士們。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n今晚同聽日 機場同街頭見</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c6iqOfx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc6iqOfx.png&h=ca29d14a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xtcWatT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxtcWatT.jpg&h=ba8a794d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t7JBUVy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft7JBUVy.jpg&h=656d6305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1B3uvvp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1B3uvvp.jpg&h=86caf1af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bae05cb56669b2e89973e701c57c3e4b05bb0ec7","tid":1439553,"uid":292011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"712357f8c30e018d3a81326d2ca5c408f4283ca6","tid":1439553,"uid":105699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:58:08.000Z","msg":"同埋今日咁撚熱，比Ｄ狗狗熱下，我地去涼冷氣重好啦～冇謂辛苦自己～"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:34:19.000Z","msg":"正！"},{"pid":"ddbc88fc6339f5121b20f04dd9e8f2de447088f7","tid":1439553,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:44:39.000Z","msg":"支持"}]}